{"tid":2269071,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"元朗劈友補習社","createTime":"2020-11-03T08:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T09:27:25.000Z","uid":214305,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6bca274cc92ec3ea62b8300c645b36fe262e1498","tid":2269071,"uid":214305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"高佬好！阿叻好！泉叔好！<br />\n來共我共商<br />\n保家安邦的態度<br />\n<br />\n鄉紳中誰又要<br />\n城內動粗？<br />\n圍住打仔變被告<br />\n<br />\n膠通、鐵棍、鞭，未分到<br />\n葉虎車箱找得到<br />\n飛天南瞓低，救得到<br />\n賣個瓜都話要把刀<br />\n<br />\n元朗國無曬巡警？打佢老母！<br />\n然後你也去醫院，扮晒擋刀又count數<br />\n若劈友亦是建制派必修一課<br />\n盼望能前來提佢著草<br />\n免到時牢內大聲哭訴<br />\n<br />\n- - -<br />\n<br />\n香港好！大灣好！習總好！<br />\n來共我研討<br />\n保家安邦的態度<br />\n<br />\n鄉紳中誰又要<br />\n盡快著草？<br />\n明明西區會認數<br />\n<br />\n膠通、鐵棍、鞭，PAT係度<br />\n搭下個膊走得到<br />\n交通費那邊，有幫補<br />\n賣個瓜都漏夜著草<br />\n<br />\n白襯衫人強馬精，追打老母<br />\n然後你也去更衣，返村派錢又啱數<br />\n若劈友亦是圍頭裡必修一課<br />\n盼望能前來提佢著草<br />\n免到時牢內大聲哭訴<br />\n<br />\nWhite shirt give me love~ <br />\nPopo give me love~<br />\nCarrie give love~<br />\nCommunist give love~<br />\nSo let us feel what is love!"},{"pid":"f4376bc7dca6c92e940b7b4aaf1b00616f9eb681","tid":2269071,"uid":18337,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNbAzxY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNbAzxY.jpg&h=653acd0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7590aeeb7fb4d769192a9012590022d2c47f84d","tid":2269071,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:50:26.000Z","msg":"新詩泥？😂"},{"pid":"5c0c360a70bf985d5b2bf4a606db1d8821dad1f9","tid":2269071,"uid":126226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最近好多新教會咁WO"},{"pid":"175d85d60435f090ff52cb716f39d408f28381aa","tid":2269071,"uid":226622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s